
[1]neglectful

   NEGLECTFUL, a.

   1. Heedless; careless; inattentive.

   2. Accustomed or apt to omit what may or ought to be done.

   3. Treating with neglect or slight.

   4. Indicating neglect, slight or indifference; as a neglectful
   countenance.
